<module status="bronze">
    <h>simple verbs</h>
    <p>Simple verbs are <a href="?xx=verbs/verbs">verbs</a> that are not formed from other
        words.</p>
    <p>List of irregular verbs – <ul>
            <li><a href="?gd=rach"><g>rach</g></a>
                <en>go</en></li>
            <li><a href="?gd=thig"><g>thig</g></a>
                <en>come</en></li>
            <li><a href="?gd=thoir"><g>thoir</g></a>
                <en>give, take, bring</en></li>
        </ul>
    </p>

